title: SPAIN 1808-1975 Raymond Carr
description:
RAYMOND CARR       "SPAIN 1808-1975"




The most read book on the issue , produced in Oxford UK 1966 (very first edition).

Is it possible to say that the book trascends the history of Spain , becoming a 

magnific example of historiography.




Today you will not find this kind of things because passion has been replaced by 

burocracy , both in universities (publish or perish) and in life in general.
